headline: Fifth Third Recognized Among 2025 Top Workplaces by USA Today
summary: CINCINNATI, April 23, 2025--For the fourth consecutive year, Fifth Third (Nasdaq: FITB) is honored to have earned the 2025 USA TODAY Top Workplaces award.
